sources.title: Dear Caroline (1968, History) French Movie by Denys de La Patellière | Starring France Anglade
sources.description:
Against the backdrop of the French revolution, young Caroline tries to reunite with her first love, despite her arranged marriage to an older politician.

Original title: Caroline chérie (1968)

This film is available with French Audio, and subtitles in many languages.

Director: Denys de La Patellière
Writer: Jacques Laurent
Stars: France Anglade, Vittorio De Sica, Bernard Blier, Karin Dor
Genres: French Cinema, Drama, History

Music by Georges Garvarentz
Lyrics by Charles Aznavour
Performed by Charles Aznavour
